@oneworldnyc is the perfect place to go for the holidays. Have drinks at the bar with an amazing view. Link in my bio + code claire22 for $5 off your tickets #OneWorldObservatory #OneWorldNYCPartner

A new year and a little over 2 years in nyc 💙 3 apartments, countless new experiences, so many opportunities and good times, but also hard ones. This year challenged me and provided so much growth. I think social media can sometimes be confusing when you often see recaps of only highlights. So here’s your reminder that everyone had lows, too. Grateful and excited to see what this year brings
